{
  "stem": "22959.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans' goal was to eliminate the Jews in particular, and the minorities in general.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in order to achieve this goal, they had two tasks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One was to eliminate all the intellectuals-- the teachers, then the students, the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] all, all the elements.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In other words, all the elements who were capable to resist and to organize, they eliminated them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they formed ghettos.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The ghetto is a certain part of town where all the Jews from all over town they were pushed into this particular area.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That means that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they had a list of all the intellectuals in our town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where did they get the list?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They got it from the local authorities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The local authorities who lived in our town, they knew all the Jews who lived in, in, in Zhetel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They made a list.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A matter of fact, that my father was also on the list.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they came-- I remember they came to my house, and they asked for my father.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father was a weak person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was-- he had problems with his, his-- I guess he had, like, you would say today, emphysema, or something like that, that he had difficulty-- he developed in this-- in his later years an allergy.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was known in town as he suffered from it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So then they came and they asked for him, we came out with my mother and with my sister and brother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we said that he's sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we saved my father for a little longer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They took all the people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They gathered them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They put them into trucks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were driven away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they were never seen again.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
